---
// SimoneCallout — homepage "Built by / on the team's own production"
// callout per v5 plan §4.1. Visually different register from
// testimonial cards so it can't be confused with customer testimony.
---

<aside class="simone-callout" aria-label="Engineering team note">
  <span class="callout-eyebrow">From the team's own production</span>
  <p class="callout-body">
    <strong>Simone Scarduzio</strong> (founder, Beshu Tech) is
    migrating ReadonlyREST's <strong>1.71 TB</strong> build catalog
    through DeltaGlider. The case study includes the bugs we hit
    (TMPDIR hardcoded in upstream, Traefik 60s timeout, pipefail+head
    silent abort, EBS exhaustion) and how we fixed them.
  </p>
  <p class="callout-cta">
    <a href="/case-studies/readonlyrest-builds">Read the migration log →</a>
  </p>
</aside>

<style>
  .simone-callout {
    max-width: var(--measure-wide);
    margin: 2rem 0;
    padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
    background: var(--ink-900);
    color: var(--ink-100);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .callout-eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .callout-body {
    color: var(--ink-100);
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .callout-body strong {
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .callout-cta {
    margin: 1rem 0 0 0;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .callout-cta a {
    color: var(--teal-300);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
  }

  .callout-cta a:hover {
    color: var(--teal-200);
    border-bottom-color: var(--teal-300);
  }
</style>
